{"tid":687556,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"節目硬銷自家App　無綫被罰30萬","createTime":"2018-06-02T11:14:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T12:43:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3ef34c9fbf500b1d1158838a20f0663c0ad00b4c","tid":687556,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T11:14:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180602/20408918\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180602%2F20408918&d=mrgUYd5Ed7UwA6vG9LKaBWxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=e071d643\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180602%2F20408918&h=a166c03d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180602/20408918</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月02日 <br />\n<br />\n節目硬銷自家App　無綫被罰30萬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180602/large/02la6p41.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180602%2Flarge%2F02la6p41.jpg&h=2867a4b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■無綫於節目中推介Big Big Channel，被指節目與廣告混合。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】無綫再因「踩界賣廣告」被罰，通訊事務管理局裁定無綫去年在五個節目中推廣自家新手機應用程式「Big Big Channel」屬間接宣傳，分別判罰款30萬元及嚴重警告。而對於無綫兩個台慶節目宣傳片中出現藝人試食及稱讚食品鏡頭，則發出強烈勸喻。<br />\n<br />\n通訊局接獲37宗投訴，指無綫翡翠台在去年6月至10月先後在《Big Big小明星2017》、《原來Big Big Channel咁好玩》、《群星拱照Big Big Channel》、《Big Big Channel失驚無神賀中秋》及《東張西望》等節目中介紹新推出手機App，將節目與廣告混合。<br />\n<br />\n無綫辯稱新App是免費電視服務的延伸，公眾可免費下載，但通訊局認為Big Big Channel獨立於無綫，提供的內容與免費電視無關，與節目無關的廣告材料應與節目清楚區分，裁定當中四個播放日期相當接近的節目一併罰款30萬元，另一個違規較輕的節目則發出嚴重警告。<br />\n<br />\n通訊局亦接獲兩宗投訴，指出去年11月《萬千星輝賀台慶》和今年1月的《萬千星輝頒獎典禮2017》宣傳片，均出現食品攤位，部份藝人進食、揮動及稱讚某食品。通訊局認為雖然宣傳片時間不長，藝人無說品牌名稱，但鏡頭可清楚看到品牌，效果等同間接宣傳，決定向無綫發出強烈勸喻。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無綫稱通訊局偏頗不公<br />\n<br />\n無綫發言人回應稱，通訊局裁決偏頗及不公平，部份節目出現有關商業品牌名稱的畫面，轉瞬即逝，有關鏡頭亦極為簡短且表達自然。Big Big Channel只為無綫免費電視服務的網上延伸，只提供與無綫相關的娛樂及資訊，不構成廣告材料，今次裁決又再凸顯通訊局主觀判斷。<br />\n<br />\n■記者麥志榮  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n專家稱死者報復心強<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n何志平上訴　申推翻拒保釋裁決"},{"pid":"80fcc0494ec492acec4dadc799819e4638a8afdc","tid":687556,"uid":157197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T11:15:44.000Z","msg":"真係好撚戇鳩"},{"pid":"8b8358062e26946d7f1971c03c04f2889ad07079","tid":687556,"uid":19055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T11:17:34.000Z","msg":"熄左電視冇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一台獨大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94786756b036ed6e2c8d18a5dfb5a8bba1dccbe8","tid":687556,"uid":34189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T11:20:04.000Z","msg":"mytv super, big dick shop果D呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最好罰埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc772ba13cbfb73fe4413e677fd12f68adb2df73","tid":687556,"uid":4574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T11:21:26.000Z","msg":"罰得太少<br />\n每播一秒罰三十萬就差唔多"},{"pid":"7044ea446124c1fd4cbac39ba4eeb5636b48b8b6","tid":687556,"uid":129340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T11:22:35.000Z","msg":"App帶黎既收入&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;300K"},{"pid":"2dbb81a5ab759510377fab73d20b6b6ede40cbed","tid":687556,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T11:53:17.000Z","msg":"記得舊時期大台，係另立一間企業，經營與電視廣播無關嘅業務。<br />\n該企業曾經坐擁零售、出版、旅遊等業務。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"737fbc67b472a93480ead6d9a0bcf0d59a724ce3","tid":687556,"uid":170383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T12:18:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"